Package: flame
Title: Functional and Literature Analysis of Multi-omics Enrichment
Version: 2.5.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Evangelos", "Karatzas", email = "karatzas@fleming.gr", role = "aut"),
    person("Fotis A.", "Baltoumas", email = "baltoumas@fleming.gr", role = "aut"),
    person("Georgios A.", "Pavlopoulos", email = "pavlopoulos@fleming.gr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: A comprehensive platform for functional enrichment analysis
    supporting multiple tools (gProfiler, STRING, enrichR, WebGestalt,
    PANTHER, GeneCodis) with interactive visualizations including bar charts,
    scatter plots, dot plots, heatmaps, and network diagrams. Supports
    gene list input, volcano plot selection, and 2D reduction plot selection.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/pavlopouloslab/flame
BugReports: https://github.com/pavlopouloslab/flame/issues
